    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>BarCampBoston2 Programming Contest entries: Pixels to Penguins</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/425620191/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="BarCampBoston2 Programming Contest entries: Pixels to Penguins" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/186/425620191_a2e3b7d205_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>By Aron of <a href="http://www.spotstory.com/">Spot Story</a>.  Takes a text entry, finds related tags, loads photos with those tags into an image of Tux, and plays a MIDI track based on it.  Won first place in the contest.</p>
        </p>

